snippet.textDisplay: Virus (when I was studying medicine MANY years ago) could NOT just "jump" across the animal/human barrier. Think of cells as locks and a virus as a key. Animal and human cells were "locked" by their structures.  Someone had to "manipulate" either the lock or the key to make them compatible...so what has changed?!
